// Thin wrapper: we ship the real design-system reference as a static HTML
// prototype under public/design-system/index.html so that we don't have to
// escape its inline styles / template literals for Astro's parser. This
// Astro route exists so that `/design-system/` (with Astro's trailing slash
// policy) resolves and forwards to the static build.
return Astro.redirect("/design-system/index.html");
